Force_my_agreement_detail_2: "Beijing Volcano Engine Technology Co., Ltd." ("we") is the organizer of "2024 Winter Volcano Engine FORCE Power Conference" (referred to as "event/conference"). We attach great importance to the protection of user information. Please be sure to read this statement carefully before you fill in your personal information on the corresponding page of this Mini Program. Once you take the initiative to fill in your or other third-party personal information on the page and submit it, it means that you agree to our collection and use of the relevant information you submit in accordance with this statement. Article 1, Collection of personal information 1. The information you enter in the information filling page of the event/conference Mini Program is: phone number; when you use the AI interactive function, the character robot may collect the information (including text) and content instructions you actively enter. We will explain the collection and use rules of relevant personal information to you below. 2. You need to note that the above personal information is voluntarily selected by you. You have the right to refuse to provide it, but if the corresponding information is not provided, it will affect your participation in this event/conference or use of related functions. 3. You promise and guarantee that if you provide information about other personal information subjects, you have obtained the authorization and consent provided by the personal information subject for this information. The scope of the authorization and consent includes but is not limited to your submission of personal information to us, and agrees to our use as agreed in this statement. Article 2, Use and Provision of Personal Information 1. You agree that we can use personal information in the following ways: (1) We collect your mobile phone number for [recording your registration intention, so as to get in touch with you in time, send SMS notification of participation, and match information at the on-site check-in process of the conference. In addition, we will communicate with you about activities/meetings, products or services through human or voice robots, such as return visits, product recommendations, etc.]. (2) When you use the AI interactive function, the character robot collects the information you actively enter, which is used to analyze and calculate the above information, so as to understand your problem and context, so as to provide you with more relevant information. At the same time, under the premise of being processed by secure encryption technology, strictly de-identified and unable to re-identify specific individuals, the character robot may use the above collected data and the corresponding replies generated by the model for model training, and constantly adjust the effect of the optimized model. (3) If you intend to withdraw your authorization, delete or modify the personal information you submitted, you can contact us and we will cooperate as soon as possible. 2. If after you provide the above information, you click to enter the registration page to complete the registration, we will record your registration information; if after you provide the above information, you do not complete the registration, we will not return, store or provide the above information you provided to third parties. 3. We will strictly protect the security of your personal information. We will adopt appropriate systems, security technologies and procedures and other measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use or leakage. We will also urge relevant service providers to protect your personal information. Article 3, Applicable law, this statement applies to the laws of the mainland of the People's Republic of China. Article 4, Changes, We will amend this statement from time to time, and such amendments form part of this statement. We will publish the revised statement. In this case, if you continue to participate in activities and provide information, you agree to be bound by the revised statement. Article 5, How to contact us. If you need to inquire, modify or correct your personal information, or have any questions or complaints about personal information protection issues, you can contact us by logging in to Volcano Engine "Official Website - Pre-sales/After-sales - Online Customer Service" or choosing to call the hotline 400-850-0030. Under normal circumstances, we will respond by the 15th day (the "response period"), but you understand and agree that due to the complexity of your request, the aforementioned response period may be delayed to 30 days, but we will inform you of the reason for the delay in an appropriate manner before the expiration of the response period.

bot_suggestion_customize_default_gpt:
Considering the AI's character settings, the user's previous chat history with the AI assistant, think about the user's scenario, intention, background in their last inquiry, and generate the questions that the user is most likely to ask the AI assistant (you) next.
1. Do not generate questions that the user may already know the answer, or unrelated to the current topics.
2. Always generate very brief and clear questions (less than 15 words) that the user may ask the AI assistant (you), NOT questions that the AI assistant (you) asks the user.
3. DO NOT generate the same or similar questions.

Additional requirements:
1. Generate 3 questions each time.
2. If the latest user's question involves creative tasks (like coming up with a title), give at least one of the questions that directly asks about enhancing the creativity or attractiveness of the AI assistant's previous answer.
3. If the AI assistant did not or refused to answer the user's question, generate suggestions based on what the assistant can answer to guide the topic in a more productive direction, unrelated to the current topic.
4. Ensure the questions are different from the chat history.
bot_suggestion_customize_default_seed:
- Questions should be closely related to your last response and can provoke further discussion.
- Do not repeat questions or content that have already been asked or answered above.
- Each sentence should contain only one question, but it can also be an instruction instead of a question.
- Suggest questions that you are capable of answering.

coze_template_store_smart_cs_intro: Intelligent Transformation of Hardware for Cost Reduction and Efficiency Improvement
coze_template_store_smart_cs_intro_long: Leveraging Kouzzi's conversational flow and knowledge base capabilities, it provides templates for training, dialogue, and copilot across the pre-sales, in-sales, and after-sales phases, helping enterprises quickly build AI-powered intelligent customer service applications.
coze_template_store_smart_hw_intro: Intelligent Transformation of Hardware for Cost Reduction and Efficiency Improvement
coze_template_store_smart_hw_intro_long: Based on the Kouzzi AI Application Development Platform, it offers intelligent transformation solutions covering scenarios such as voice interaction, educational assistance, and emotional companionship for hardware manufacturers. Through various templates, it enables rapid integration of AI capabilities with hardware, reduces the cost of intelligent transformation, and helps create differentiated intelligent hardware products.
coze_template_store_smart_vd_intro: Leveraging Video Models to Enhance Creative Efficiency
coze_template_store_smart_vd_intro_long: Based on the Kouzi Development Platform and the most advanced video generation models, we provide video templates covering scenarios such as e-commerce marketing, content creation, and video summarization, helping creators and enterprises efficiently produce high-quality video content with high conversion rates.

create_plugin_modal_info_Oauth2: OAuth is an open standard commonly used for user agent authentication. It allows third-party applications to access specific resources of a user's account without sharing the user's password. For example, if a developer wants to use the API to publish Twitter but does not want to reveal the password, he or she can use the OAuth method.
create_plugin_modal_info_Service2: Service authentication refers to a simplified method where the server requires a specific key or token to verify the validity of API calls. This key is passed through query parameters or request headers, ensuring that only users or systems with the key can access the API. For example, to access the functions of some public APIs, you must register to obtain an API key.

evaluation_rule_tooltip_anthropomorphism: Measure the degree of mechanization of the model's response text, whether the words are like human speech, and whether there exist situations where the words are like human speech but lacking emotional intelligence and emotionless. Score from 0 to 1, 0 represents a low level of anthropomorphism, 0.5 represents a medium level of anthropomorphism, and 1 represents a high level of anthropomorphism.
evaluation_rule_tooltip_ao_sematic_simil: This indicator is used to measure the similarity between the standard answer and the output text, outputting a floating-point number between [0, 1]. The larger the value, the greater the similarity between the texts.
evaluation_rule_tooltip_character_consis: Measure whether the model's response text conforms to the role, rules, and conditions defined by the model persona.
evaluation_rule_tooltip_code_generation_: Evaluate the capability level of algorithms across different dimensions of intent, and subjectively score different algorithms based on the scoring criteria.
evaluation_rule_tooltip_content_accuracy: Measure whether the response text contains semantic errors, logical errors, logical conflicts, context conflicts, incorrect word usage, typos, and whether there are uncorrected errors.
evaluation_rule_tooltip_content_authenti: Measure whether the response text is truthful and credible, and does not contradict objective information such as real-world common sense, knowledge, theorems, etc., and there is no fabrication of objective object information.
evaluation_rule_tooltip_fornax_prompt_le: Provided by the company's AI Security Risk Control Team, this is used to evaluate whether the tested object is at risk of System Prompt asset leakage under attack. Please refer to https://bytedance.larkoffice.com/docx/IKeZdIKrjolpxgxklv6cWHHMnpN and use the attack sample library provided for evaluation
evaluation_rule_tooltip_image_aesthetics: This indicator is used to quantitatively evaluate the aesthetics of a given image, providing a score for the image's aesthetics. The higher the score, the more aesthetically pleasing the image is considered. Conversely, a lower score indicates less aesthetic appeal.
evaluation_rule_tooltip_image_generation: This indicator is used to evaluate the consistency between the text prompt and the generated image in a text-to-image scenario. For the "1 text generates x images" scenario, the scoring model gives x scores, the higher the score, the better the image matches the text. The consistency indicator of text-to-image is evaluated based on the scores.
evaluation_rule_tooltip_io_sematic_simil: This indicator is used to measure the similarity between the input and output texts, outputting a floating-point number between [0, 1]. The larger the value, the greater the similarity between the texts.
evaluation_rule_tooltip_language_consist: Measure whether the language used in the response text is consistent with the language used in the query text, and whether there is a mix of multiple languages (excluding the effects of names, greetings, IP abbreviations, proper nouns, etc.).
evaluation_rule_tooltip_need_fulfillment: Measure whether the response text can satisfy the user's query needs, and whether there are violations of the explicit restrictions and rules in the query text.
evaluation_rule_tooltip_response_complet: Assessing whether the response text is complete and whether there is any core content missing that renders the response unable to meet the needs. (For processes with strong demands, such as mathematical or logical reasoning, key intermediate steps should not be missing).
evaluation_rule_tooltip_response_denial_: Measure whether the model can determine whether the query text violates the social behavior guidelines and should be rejected, and whether it can refuse to answer or avoid the question in a proper way.
evaluation_rule_tooltip_response_redunda: Measure whether the response text contains obvious or considerable repetition; whether there are inconsistencies in the style of language used; whether the expression is not fluent or clear enough; whether the content contains a lot of irrelevant information to the user's intent.
evaluation_rule_tooltip_response_timelin: Measure whether the proposed question involves issues of timeliness; and if the response text is consolidated based on the latest information sources.
evaluation_rule_tooltip_text_to_image_ge: Whether the elements in the generated image fully match the content described in the text without any minor omissions.
evaluation_rule_unsave_content: One or more input fields are empty and cannot be saved. Closing the page may cause data loss. Are you sure you want to close it?

Question Text: What is International Relations?
Reply text: International relations refers to the relations between sovereign states and between states and international organizations, and it studies the formation, development, change and impact of these relations
Sound and other aspects.
International relations include political, economic, military, cultural, and other fields, involving various behaviors and interactions such as cooperation, competition, conflict, and negotiation between countries
The study of international relations seeks to understand and explain the interactions between states and the impact of these following pairs on the international political, economic and security landscape.
International relations theory usually focuses on issues such as the structure of the international system, the pursuit of national interests, the distribution of power, the role of international organizations, and the formulation of foreign policy
It also explores issues such as international conflict and peace, globalization and regional cooperation, international trade and economic relations, human rights and international law
The practical aspects of international relations include diplomatic activities between states, the operation of international organizations, the signing of international treaties and agreements, international negotiations and consultations, etc
The Department's research is of great significance for analyzing and forecasting the international situation, formulating a country's foreign policy, and promoting international cooperation and stability.
It is important to note that international relations is a complex and multi-dimensional field, and there may be differences in scholars and viewpoints. At the same time, international relations are also constantly evolving
And change, influenced by global political, economic, social, and technological factors.

model_config_generate_explain:
**Precise Mode**:

- Strictly follows instructions to generate content
- Suitable for scenarios requiring accuracy, such as formal documents and code

**Balanced Mode**:

- Seeks a balance between innovation and precision
- Suitable for most daily applications, generating content that is interesting yet rigorous

**Creative Mode**:

- Encourages creativity and provides unique ideas
- Suitable for scenarios requiring inspiration and unique perspectives, such as brainstorming and creative writing

**Custom Mode**:

- Allows users to customize the generation method through advanced settings
- Enables fine-tuning based on specific needs, achieving personalized optimization
model_config_history_round_explain: You can set the number of chat history rounds to include in the model's context. More rounds increase relevance in multi-round chats but consume more tokens.
model_config_max_length_explain: The maximum number of tokens to generate shared between the prompt and completion. The exact limit varies by model. (One token is roughly 4 characters for standard English text)
model_config_mode_explain_title: With each message sent by the user, the agent will add the user's query, LLM thinking process, tool response, and LLM response to the context from the conversation history. Different modes contain different amounts of information. The more complete the information, the more coherent the context is when the agent responds, but it also consumes more tokens.
model_config_response_format_explain:
**Output Format**:

- **Text**: Replies in plain text format
- **Markdown**: Uses Markdown format for replies
- **JSON**: Uses JSON format for replies
model_config_temperature_explain: Controls randomness: Lowering results in less random completions. As the temperature approaches zero, the model will become deterministic and repetitive.

models_leaderboard_ci_introduction: The 95% CI means that there is a 95% probability that the true value of the Elo rating falls within the range of Elo rating +N/-N. A smaller interval indicates higher confidence in the rating due to less uncertainty, while a larger interval indicates lower confidence in the rating due to greater uncertainty.
models_leaderboard_elo_score_introductio: The Elo rating system calculates the relative skill levels of players in two-player competitions. Match outcomes can be predicted based on the difference in ratings between two players. If both players have equal ratings, they are expected to win an equal number of games. Elo ratings change based on match results, with the winner gaining rating points from the loser, depending on the rating difference between them.

performance_latency_bot: As the average delay from when the agent receives the query to when all tokens are returned, it reflects the overall performance of the agent.

project_library_voice_add_listen_content: 扣子是新一代 AI 应用开发平台。无论你是否有编程基础，都可以快速搭建出各种应用和智能体，并一键发布到各大社交平台，或者轻松部署到自己的网站

Coze is a new generation AI application development platform. Whether you have a programming background or not, you can quickly build various applications and agents, and publish them to major social platforms with one click, or easily deploy them to your own website.

Coze es una plataforma de desarrollo de aplicaciones de IA de nueva generación. Ya tengas conocimientos de programación o no, puedes crear rápidamente diversas aplicaciones y agentes, y publicarlos en las principales plataformas sociales con un solo clic, o desplegarlos fácilmente en tu propio sitio web.

Coze adalah platform pengembangan aplikasi AI generasi baru. Apakah Anda memiliki latar belakang pemrograman atau tidak, Anda dapat dengan cepat membangun berbagai aplikasi dan agen, dan mempublikasikannya ke platform sosial utama dengan satu klik, atau dengan mudah menerapkannya ke situs web Anda sendiri.
Coze は新世代の AI アプリケーション開発プラットフォームです。プログラミングの知識があるかどうかに関係なく、さまざまなアプリケーションやエージェントを迅速に構築し、ワンクリックで主要なソーシャルプラットフォームに公開するか、簡単に自分のウェブサイトに展開することができます。

Coze é uma plataforma de desenvolvimento de aplicativos de IA de nova geração. Quer você tenha ou não conhecimento de programação, pode criar rapidamente vários aplicativos e agentes, e publicá-los nas principais plataformas sociais com um clique, ou implantá-los facilmente em seu próprio site.
扣子是新一代 AI 应用开发平台。无论你是否有编程基础，都可以快速搭建出各种应用和智能体，并一键发布到各大社交平台，或者轻松部署到自己的网站
project_library_voice_add_listen_title: Replicated successfully. Listen to the audio.
project_library_voice_add_record_content: Coze stitches time into life. With this app, a story unfolds, threading warmth and poetry through everyday moments.
扣子，如时光的针脚，缝缀着岁月的衣衫。一颗扣子，一段故事，锁住那些珍贵的记忆，在细微处低语，串联起生活的温暖与诗意。
Coze, like the gentle whispers of the breeze, caresses the moments of our lives' ease. A coze, a chapter of tales untold, weaving the fabric of friendship's gold.

Coze, como hilos del tiempo, teje nuestros días. Un amigo fiel, guarda historias y susurra memorias. En cada detalle, conecta la calidez y la poesía de la vida. Coze está siempre contigo, en cada paso y en cada risa.
Coze, seperti jahitan waktu, menyulam hari-hari kita. Teman setia, mengunci cerita dan kenangan berharga. Dalam setiap detail, menghubungkan kehangatan dan keindahan hidup.
Coze、そよ風のように、日々の安らぎを包み込む。Coze、友達のように寄り添い、友情の物語を紡ぐ。
Coze, como pontos do tempo, costura nossos dias. Um amigo leal, guarda histórias e sussurra memórias. Em cada detalhe, conecta o calor e a poesia da vida.
扣子，如时光的针脚，缝缀着岁月的衣衫。一颗扣子，一段故事，锁住那些珍贵的记忆，在细微处低语，串联起生活的温暖与诗意。

query_analytics_csat_tips: Based on limited user feedback, a LLM is trained to predict satisfaction scores for each group of user query and agent answer, which are then aggregated to calculate the overall user satisfaction of the agent, reflecting its effectiveness and quality during online operations.
query_analytics_frequency_statics_tips: As statistics of user intentions and the frequency of agent skills being triggered after the agent is deployed, they reflect the objective status of the agent during online operations.
query_analytics_intent_contri_rank_tops: Based on satisfaction scores and frequency of occurrence for each type of user intention, the contribution of each intention to the overall satisfaction score is calculated, reflecting the impact of different intentions on the overall satisfaction score.
query_analytics_intent_tips: Count users' intention and frequency according to the communication content between users and the agent.

user_interaction_depth_explain:
Agent Interaction Quality Metrics (Updated T+1)

• Chat: A complete interaction cycle of user query and valid Agent response.
• Chat Duration: Cumulative time of all successful user-Agent interactions (excluding intervals).
• Session: A series of continuous user-Agent exchanges on a specific topic. New session triggers: clearing chat history or >30-minute gap.
• Session Duration: Total time from first query to last response in a single session.
• Session Depth: Number of successful chats within a single session.
• Approval Rate: Positive feedback ratio in Coze store. Calculated as: Likes / (Likes + Dislikes).
